{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KxJ1cVGYQT29DnbPRpzgTC","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Implementation History — 205-real-wallet\n     2→\n     3→Iteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\n     4→attempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\n     5→of every iteration to understand prior context.\n     6→\n     7→---\n     8→\n     9→## Iteration 1 — Build validation in real wallet mode\n    10→\n    11→**Item**: Set `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false`, run `pnpm build`, `pnpm lint`, and `pnpm typecheck`.\n    12→\n    13→**Result**: All three checks passed with zero errors. The pre-existing scaffold code (`RealWalletProvider.tsx`, `TestWalletProvider.tsx`, `WalletProvider.tsx`) compiles cleanly in real wallet mode. No fixes needed.\n    14→\n    15→- `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false pnpm build`: 423 modules transformed, build successful\n    16→- `pnpm lint`: 0 errors (10 pre-existing warnings in unrelated files)\n    17→- `pnpm typecheck`: 0 errors\n    18→\n    19→**Status**: Complete\n    20→## Iteration 1 — 2026-02-19T11:38:50Z — OK\n    21→- **Log**: iteration-001.log\n    22→\n    23→---\n    24→\n    25→## Iteration 2 — Shared ConnectionProvider across all wallet modes\n    26→\n    27→**Item**: Move `ConnectionProvider` from `RealWalletProvider.tsx` to `WalletProvider.tsx` level.\n    28→\n    29→**Changes**:\n    30→- `packages/wallet/src/WalletProvider.tsx` — Added `ConnectionProvider` import from `@solana/wallet-adapter-react`, added `getRpcUrl()` helper (reads `VITE_RPC_URL`, defaults to `https://api.devnet.solana.com`), wrapped both Mock and Real provider branches with `<ConnectionProvider endpoint={endpoint}>`.\n    31→- `packages/wallet/src/real/RealWalletProvider.tsx` — Removed `ConnectionProvider` import and wrapper, removed `getRpcUrl()` and `DEFAULT_RPC_URL` (now handled at `WalletProvider` level). `WalletBridge` still uses `useConnection()` from the shared provider.\n    32→\n    33→**Result**: All checks passed:\n    34→- `pnpm lint`: 0 errors\n    35→- `pnpm typecheck`: 0 errors\n    36→- `pnpm build` (mock mode): successful (423 modules)\n    37→- `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false pnpm build` (real mode): successful (423 modules)\n    38→\n    39→**Status**: Complete\n    40→\n    41→## Iteration 2 — 2026-02-19T11:42:57Z — OK\n    42→- **Log**: iteration-002.log\n    43→\n    44→---\n    45→\n    46→## Iteration 3 — CoinflipContext + useBalance use shared Connection\n    47→\n    48→**Item**: Update `CoinflipContext.tsx` and `useBalance.ts` to use `useConnection()` from the shared `ConnectionProvider` instead of creating their own `Connection` instances.\n    49→\n    50→**Changes**:\n    51→- `apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/context/CoinflipContext.tsx` — Replaced `const connection = useMemo(() => new Connection(RPC_URL, \"confirmed\"), [])` with `const { connection } = useConnection()`. Deleted the `RPC_URL` constant and removed `useMemo`/`Connection` imports. Import `useConnection` from `@rng-utopia/wallet/hooks`.\n    52→- `packages/wallet/src/useBalance.ts` — Replaced internal `connectionRef`, `getConnection()`, `getRpcUrl()`, and `DEFAULT_RPC_URL` with `const { connection } = useConnection()`. Removed `Connection` import and the `rpcUrl` option from `UseBalanceOptions`. Removed the `connectionRef` cleanup effect.\n    53→- `packages/wallet/src/hooks.ts` — Re-exported `useConnection` from `@solana/wallet-adapter-react` so consumers (like CoinflipContext) don't need a direct dependency.\n    54→\n    55→**Result**: All checks passed:\n    56→- `pnpm lint`: 0 errors (10 pre-existing warnings)\n    57→- `pnpm typecheck`: 0 errors\n    58→- `pnpm build` (mock mode): successful (423 modules)\n    59→- `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false pnpm build` (real mode): successful (423 modules)\n    60→\n    61→**Status**: Complete\n    62→\n    63→## Iteration 3 — 2026-02-19T11:47:30Z — OK\n    64→- **Log**: iteration-003.log\n    65→\n    66→---\n    67→\n    68→## Iteration 4 — Mock mode + visual regression preservation\n    69→\n    70→**Item**: Run `pnpm test:visual` — all 17 visual regression baselines pass with zero diff. Verify zero JS console errors in mock mode via Playwright headless.\n    71→\n    72→**Result**: All 17 visual regression tests passed (12 route baselines + 5 state variants). The `stablePage` fixture collects console errors and fails tests on any errors — all tests passed, confirming zero JS console errors. No code changes needed — this iteration validates that iterations 1-3 (wallet refactor) preserved mock mode UI and behavior.\n    73→\n    74→- `pnpm test:visual`: 17 passed (1m 36s)\n    75→- Console errors: 0 (verified by `stablePage` fixture)\n    76→\n    77→**Status**: Complete\n    78→\n    79→## Iteration 4 — 2026-02-19T11:50:54Z — OK\n    80→- **Log**: iteration-004.log\n    81→\n    82→---\n    83→\n    84→## Iteration 5 — Real mode app startup validation\n    85→\n    86→**Item**: Start dev server with `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false` and `VITE_RPC_URL=https://api.devnet.solana.com`. Load app in Playwright headless — verify no JS console errors, wallet icon renders disconnected, clicking wallet icon calls `connect()` without crashing.\n    87→\n    88→**Changes**:\n    89→- `apps/platform/playwright.real.config.ts` — New Playwright config for real-mode tests. Starts Vite dev server on port 3001 with `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false` and `VITE_RPC_URL=https://api.devnet.solana.com` via webServer `env` property. Only matches `real/**/*.spec.ts`.\n    90→- `apps/platform/e2e/real/startup.spec.ts` — New test file with `realPage` fixture (console error collection, no frozen time/randomness). Two tests: (1) app loads without console errors, wallet icon visible in disconnected state with \"—\" text; (2) clicking wallet icon triggers connect() without crashing, app remains functional.\n    91→- `apps/platform/package.json` — Added `test:real` script (`playwright test --config playwright.real.config.